{"title":"山城的一枝红梅——参观石评梅故居有感","authors":["晓晴"],"dates":[{"year":1992,"month":5,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"山城的一枝红梅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——参观石评梅故居有感"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晓晴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在山城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在姑姑寺街"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这条古老的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石板小路上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又落满了雪花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在圣洁的白雪中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一枝红梅归故里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梅花素雅质丽、含笑无语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"携着陶然亭忠贞的思恋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为故乡撒一片晶莹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我读她雪里的诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读她诗里的梅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读她冰霜里的散文"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读这位孤傲人世的女性"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掬一泓腊梅花蕊的底蕴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古老蜿蜒的石板小路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧系着空空的院落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冠山萧瑟鸣一阵松涛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送一丝甜甜的山风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"静谧的平定山城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每天在等待自己养育的女儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"企盼冰清玉洁的梅魂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这梅花和雪花铺满的石径上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘然而至"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}